or a bunch of baked D&D players

34:14.139 --> 34:16.532
rioting after
their wizard dies.

34:16.576 --> 34:17.838
- Yeah, you also never hear,

34:17.881 --> 34:20.797
"Stoned doctor nails
brain surgery."

34:23.191 --> 34:25.411
- Okay.

34:25.454 --> 34:28.718
I can see you don't wanna have
a serious conversation.

34:31.156 --> 34:32.635
- Where'd you go?

34:32.679 --> 34:35.464
- I just had
to go grab $20,000.

34:35.508 --> 34:37.075
Now where's Brandy?

34:38.076 --> 34:39.860
- [laughs]
En garde!

34:39.903 --> 34:41.122
[laughs]

34:41.166 --> 34:43.864
- Eww!
- I'm sure she washed it.

34:43.907 --> 34:45.170
[laughs]

34:45.213 --> 34:47.520
- Dude, is that
your mom's dildo?

34:47.563 --> 34:50.088
- [laughs]

34:50.131 --> 34:51.828
- Stop!
- Dude, that's not really--

34:51.872 --> 34:55.136
- Lex, stop!
- Oh, my God, dude.

34:55.180 --> 34:58.705
- Scoot off, you tit!
- I've read your file.

34:58.748 --> 35:00.185
Your dad's not some
tough gangster!

35:00.228 --> 35:02.752
You're just this
lowly ------- Rat

35:02.796 --> 35:04.798
who came from a dock worker.

35:04.841 --> 35:06.016
- What did you say?

35:06.060 --> 35:07.583
[dramatic music]

35:07.627 --> 35:11.979
Don't you ever talk
about my dad again,

35:12.022 --> 35:14.503
you yuppie piece of shit!

35:14.547 --> 35:16.070
Take your mother's dong!

35:16.114 --> 35:19.900
Eat your mother's...dong.

35:24.034 --> 35:25.949
----!

35:25.993 --> 35:29.649
[clapping]
- [laughs]

35:29.692 --> 35:33.043
There is old KGB wisdom.

35:33.087 --> 35:35.568
Sometimes you are dildo,

35:35.611 --> 35:37.787
and sometimes you are face.

35:37.831 --> 35:39.137
- Cops!

35:39.180 --> 35:41.791
[distant sirens blaring]

35:55.283 --> 35:58.982
- [laughing]

35:59.026 --> 36:00.506
What's the matter, buddy?
- Shut up!

36:00.549 --> 36:02.682
- [laughs]
- [groans]

36:02.725 --> 36:06.990
- [laughing]

36:08.862 --> 36:10.646
- Hah, tell you what, Chico.

36:10.690 --> 36:12.561
Chick like that does definitely
know how to party.

36:12.605 --> 36:13.910
- Just getting started, compa.

36:13.954 --> 36:15.782
Got the penthouse
at the perma.

36:15.825 --> 36:18.785
- Oof.
I'm busy, you know what I mean?

36:18.828 --> 36:19.786
Can't wait.

36:19.829 --> 36:26.836
♪

36:28.751 --> 36:30.579
- Don't mind if I do.

36:30.623 --> 36:34.148
- Mmm, we're gonna dance
until the sun comes up.

36:34.192 --> 36:35.758
[gunshot]

36:35.802 --> 36:38.239
- [shuddering]

36:38.283 --> 36:39.980
[breathing heavily]

36:40.023 --> 36:44.550
- Make it disappear?
- Tell my old man it's done.

36:44.593 --> 36:45.899
- On it.

36:50.556 --> 36:53.123
- [breathing heavily]

37:07.225 --> 37:09.227
- I love you.

37:09.270 --> 37:12.099
But you needed a reminder
of who I am, baby.

37:17.365 --> 37:19.976
I know about Marcus.

37:20.020 --> 37:24.546
Tricking that psycho Rat
to take me out?

37:26.679 --> 37:29.725
- [crying]

37:32.380 --> 37:34.034
[crying]

37:34.077 --> 37:37.167
- Hey.

37:37.211 --> 37:39.169
[speaking Spanish]

37:39.213 --> 37:42.912
Relax.

37:42.956 --> 37:47.221
You're gonna be my wife.

37:47.265 --> 37:50.006
You're gonna raise up my niños.

37:50.050 --> 37:51.878
You know I'd never kill you.

37:51.921 --> 37:53.619
- [sniffs]

37:53.662 --> 37:58.276
- But you do some shit
like that again,

37:58.319 --> 38:00.930
and you're gonna wish I did.

38:09.417 --> 38:12.638
- [crying]

38:20.254 --> 38:21.864
[birds chirping]

38:25.912 --> 38:28.741
[clanging]

38:28.784 --> 38:29.785
- Get dressed.

38:43.930 --> 38:46.280
- Your dad was the last
of a dying breed.

38:46.324 --> 38:51.024
Wh--when grandma got the
Alzheimer's, he was there.

38:51.067 --> 38:53.592
Then when she finally died,

38:53.635 --> 38:55.507
some--something
broke inside him.

38:55.550 --> 38:57.944
- I thought you might
have known him.

38:57.987 --> 39:00.816
- And my dad never came back.

39:00.860 --> 39:02.122
[crying]

39:02.165 --> 39:04.516
No world he deserved
would happened.

39:07.997 --> 39:10.783
Oh, it doesn't matter now.

39:10.826 --> 39:12.262
He's gone.

39:15.962 --> 39:17.920
You're with your mom again,
Dad.

39:32.631 --> 39:34.763
Who is he?

39:45.034 --> 39:49.604
- Rory and me lived in
a shanty camp under a bridge.

39:51.040 --> 39:54.087
He was always, uh...

39:54.130 --> 39:55.610
[sighs]

40:00.136 --> 40:01.224
He--

40:13.323 --> 40:16.631
He was the worst
piece of shit I ever knew.

40:16.675 --> 40:22.681
He stole and he beat up women
and he hurt people.

40:22.724 --> 40:24.117
[dramatic music]

40:24.160 --> 40:26.249
Whatever happened to him,
whoever he was,

40:26.293 --> 40:29.383
I don't give a shit

40:29.427 --> 40:34.693
because he chose who he became,

40:34.736 --> 40:36.216
and who he became was terrible.

40:36.259 --> 40:43.266
♪

40:44.311 --> 40:45.704
- [spits]

40:45.747 --> 40:48.054
You burn in hell,
you asshole.

40:48.097 --> 40:55.104
♪

40:59.979 --> 41:01.284
- Why'd you do that?

41:01.328 --> 41:03.417
♪

41:03.461 --> 41:05.724
- It's important
we face our victims.

41:05.767 --> 41:12.774
♪

41:14.297 --> 41:18.127
- I told myself all day
I didn't feel anything.

41:18.171 --> 41:23.306
But once I heard his daughter,
her delusion...

41:23.350 --> 41:26.440
- We hate imagining anyone
unveiling truths about us

41:26.484 --> 41:28.747
when we pass,

41:28.790 --> 41:31.271
so we forgive others
once they do.

41:31.314 --> 41:34.927
♪

41:34.970 --> 41:38.757
I.D.,
wanted for six homicides.

41:41.673 --> 41:44.937
Your fortitude likely
prevented many more.

41:50.812 --> 41:55.948
Those who lack backbone
are devoured.

41:55.991 --> 41:59.952
We can't expect others
to watch the herd.

41:59.995 --> 42:01.954
It's up to us.

42:05.740 --> 42:07.176
- There might have
been a better way.

42:07.220 --> 42:10.049
- Noise, noise, noise.

42:10.092 --> 42:13.966
Just something you think
you're supposed to say.

42:15.837 --> 42:18.318
- So what?

42:18.361 --> 42:21.756
I just keep pulling the trigger
as long as I believe

42:21.800 --> 42:24.933
the old man telling me
to do it is fine?

42:24.977 --> 42:26.239
Then I can live with it?

42:26.282 --> 42:29.982
- You were justified.

42:30.025 --> 42:34.247
Erasing that human stain
doesn't mean you absorb it.

42:34.290 --> 42:37.076
You made the world better.

42:37.119 --> 42:41.471
Over time, you'll see.

42:41.515 --> 42:44.083
I, for one,
am very proud of you.

42:50.306 --> 42:53.483
You deserve
a good night of sleep.

42:53.527 --> 42:57.487
We found you a permanent
room assignment.

42:57.531 --> 43:00.795
I believe you've already met
your new roommate.

43:00.839 --> 43:07.846
♪

43:17.856 --> 43:20.467
You were right.

43:20.510 --> 43:23.252
Marcus did the kill,
not Willie.

43:27.213 --> 43:30.042
You were smart to tell me.

43:30.085 --> 43:32.827
The deeds of your pledge
are yours to share.

43:32.871 --> 43:34.176
- Yes, sir.

43:37.049 --> 43:38.398
- Tell me his weaknesses.

43:39.529 --> 43:42.054
- He's a liar,
a liability with the cops,

43:42.097 --> 43:43.838
and a substance abuser.

43:45.492 --> 43:50.062
- And his greatest weakness?

43:50.105 --> 43:52.412
- His need for friends
and family.

43:52.455 --> 43:54.022
- Very good.

43:57.417 --> 43:59.941
But you're holding
something back.

44:06.034 --> 44:08.210
- Marcus didn't kill the kids
at the boys' home.

44:08.254 --> 44:10.256
His reputation is a lie.

44:10.299 --> 44:17.306
♪

44:22.877 --> 44:24.618
- So if he didn't
kill them...

44:24.662 --> 44:27.969
♪

44:28.013 --> 44:29.014
Who did?

44:29.057 --> 44:34.106
♪

44:34.149 --> 44:36.195
[thunder rumbling]

44:36.238 --> 44:39.459
[goat bleating]

44:45.160 --> 44:48.207
- [grunting]

44:52.994 --> 44:55.649
- Step away from the goat
and put your hands in the air.

44:55.693 --> 44:57.216
Freak.

44:57.259 --> 45:00.828
- Now, I'm feeling
a bit judged.

45:03.178 --> 45:05.267
I wasn't hurting no one.

45:05.311 --> 45:07.356
I was just spreading some love.

45:07.400 --> 45:09.315
[laughs]
[bricks clattering]

45:11.099 --> 45:12.840
Ooh!

45:15.321 --> 45:17.497
Sorry about your noodle.

45:17.540 --> 45:19.978
But I need a pig to help me
find the kid

45:20.021 --> 45:23.242
that torched that boys' home.

45:23.285 --> 45:27.159
[chuckles]
And, Officer?

45:27.202 --> 45:29.944
If you thought I was going
at that goat hard...

45:29.988 --> 45:34.688
♪

45:34.732 --> 45:38.692
Just wait till you see what
I do to my old pal Marcus.

45:38.736 --> 45:45.917
♪
